				"§7  The Starbuncle walks between them, transferring items continuously."
				"§7• §6Ch 5 bonus:§7 The §eStarbuncle Wheel§7 converts the Starbuncle's"
				"§7  patrol into Create Stress Units — free SU from magic rotation!"
