				"§eHow to summon your first Starbuncle:§r"
				"§7  1. Build a Ritual Circle (see The Ritual Circle quest)."
				"§7  2. Place the §6Ritual Tablet: Summon Starbuncle§7 on the Brazier."
				"§7  3. Place the ingredients listed in the Worn Notebook on candle pedestals."
				"§7  4. Have 3+ full Source Jars near the Brazier — the ritual is Source-heavy."
				"§7  5. Right-click the Brazier with a Source Gem to start the ritual."
				"§7  6. A Starbuncle spawns near the Brazier when the ritual completes."
				""
				"§7To assign a patrol path:"
				"§7  • Hold a §6Gold Stripe§7 (crafted: Gold Ingot + String)."
				"§7  • Right-click the Starbuncle, then right-click your Source Jar."
