				"§fmatching spells automatically."
				""
				"§eThe four focuses:§r"
				"§7• §cFire Focus§7 — adds §oIgnite§7 to fire spells (damage-over-time burn)."
				"§7• §bWater Focus§7 — adds §oWet§7 to water spells (slows hit targets)."
				"§7• §aEarth Focus§7 — adds §oRooted§7 to earth spells (roots targets briefly)."
				"§7• §eAir Focus§7 — adds §oLaunched§7 to air spells (sends targets airborne)."
				""
				"§eHow to equip a Focus:§r"
				"§7  1. Hold your Spellbook and press the §6Focus Slot key§7 (default: F)."
				"§7  2. Drag the Focus into the Focus Slot in the spellbook UI."
				"§7  3. All matching elemental spells now gain the secondary effect."
				"§7  4. The Focus stays permanently — it is not consumed per cast."
				""
				"§eHow to craft a Focus:§r"
				"§7Each Focus is crafted in the §6Apparatus§7 using elemental ingredients:"
				"§7  • §cFire Focus:§7 Blaze Rod + Fire Charge + Source Gems on the Apparatus."
				"§7  • §bWater Focus:§7 Prismarine Crystals + Water Bucket + Source Gems."
				"§7  • §aEarth Focus:§7 Mossy Stone Brick + Sapling + Source Gems."
				"§7  • §eAir Focus:§7 Feather × 4 + Source Gems."
				"§7(Exact ingredient layouts in JEI — search the Focus name.)"
				""
				"§eBest Focus for each playstyle:§r"
				"§7• §cFire Focus§7 — best early combat (Ignite DoT stacks on bosses)."
				"§7• §bWater Focus§7 — best for group control (Wet slows mob swarms)."
				"§7• §aEarth Focus§7 — best solo bosses (Root gives breathing room)."
				""
				"§7You can only slot ONE Focus at a time. Carry other focuses"
				"§7in a Curios Pouch for quick swapping between encounters."
				""
				"§a► Task: Have any Elemental Focus in your inventory. Not consumed."
				"§7(Any of the four element types satisfies this quest.)"
			]
