				""
				"§eWhat the Bookwyrm does:§r"
				"§7• §6Automatically casts spells§7 you designate at set intervals"
				"§7  while bound to you — hands-free spell automation."
				"§7• Draws Source from Source Gems in your inventory to fuel its casts."
				"§7• Can be assigned triggers: 'cast when in combat', 'cast while moving',"
